  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK833">
<l>nāṇāmai nāṭāmai nāriṉmai yātoṉṟum</l>
<l>pēṇāmai pētai toḻil</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Shamelessness indifference (to what must be sought after), harshness, and aversion for everything (that ought to be desired) are the qualities of the fool.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
